SummaryEnglish: Set free on Earth, fairies with magical powers begin influencing people's emotions. Now, it's up to a princess from a faraway kingdom to stop them!

1.SummaryEnglish: While Maya, Romi and Ian are filming a cooking tutorial in the bakery, Kikiping turns this cooking time into a nightmare.

2.SummaryEnglish: At school, Charmping makes everyone angry look ridiculous. Romi must catch her, but she promised Ian she would go to a concert with him!

3.SummaryEnglish: Romi has just encountered Marylou and became friend with her, when Shyping completly changes her character...

4.SummaryEnglish: While Romi's binomial for a project, Nile, is highly addicted to a video game, Romi finds Dadaping, a Royalping who makes everything possible to arrange the problem

5.SummaryEnglish: In the bakery on a normal day, Ian, Kyle, and Jun, who argued, suddenly start competiting, because of Dareping...

6.SummaryEnglish: Maya is very scared of failing in gym class. And Gogoping, who tries to arrange the situation, makes things even worse!

7.SummaryEnglish: At school, Ellie, the class representative, finds Blankping in her locker, which makes her completely forget what the teacher asked her.

8.SummaryEnglish: Marylou, who can't eat anything at the moment, is tricked by Surpriseping's illusions, who transforms normal objects into food.

9.SummaryEnglish: Maya's mom, who owns the Flower Shop, has difficulties to take care of the flowers. Meanwhile, Chachaping is looking for Princess Romi...

10.TitleEnglish: What Does a Tear Candy Taste Like?
10.SummaryEnglish: At the Heartrose Bakery, Sarah suddenly feels very bad and cries a lot. Sadping makes the whole city cries, to transform their tears into delicious candy.

11.SummaryEnglish: Moseyping is causing some trouble in the Heartrose Bakery : everyone fells tired... And more importantly, a cake has been stealed! Who is guilty? Dadaping decides to investigate

12.SummaryEnglish: Dua, who is very afraid of singing in front of all her classmates, meets Lalaping, a Royal Teenieping. As she encourages Dua, Romi finds her and catches her...

13.SummaryEnglish: Today, the famous singer Heiju is coming to Harmony Village. And Micmicping, who is a fan of her, makes the whole city dance!

14.SummaryEnglish: While everything seems normal, Marylou suddenly changes her look, because of Narrping, who gives magic mirrors to all of Romi's class.

15.SummaryEnglish: After an argument, Heartsping decides to live. She meets Luca, Marylou's sister, who takes care of her. Romi must quickly recover her!

16.SummaryEnglish: While Romi and the Royal Teeniepings are organizing a picnic, Gogoping's camera is stolen! Meanwhile, Spookping is having fun scaring everyone and create a photo collection.

17.SummaryEnglish: Tutuping, who was caught by Romi, is jealous of Heartsping, conviced that Romi only loves her. Full of jealousy, she decides to leave.

18.SummaryEnglish: For Romi's birthday, everyone is organising a surprise party for her. But by falling, Blankping makes everyone forget about the party.

19.SummaryEnglish: In a sunny and normal day, Goodping is searching for good people, as she has a very special reward to offer to them...

20.SummaryEnglish: In all Harmony Village, Tweetping has fun revealing everyone's secrets and thoughts. Romi has to quickly catch him, as he could even reveal her secret identity!

21.SummaryEnglish: Gogoping, who wants to impress everyone, has eaten so many that he became as big as the bakery! Luckily, Stella, Romi's grandmother, decides to visit Romi.

22.SummaryEnglish: While the Heartrose Bakery is organizing an event with Stella, Allmineping steals all Harmony Village's food by plugging his hand into his magic basket...

23.SummaryEnglish: Roarping, who gets angry very easily, is splashed by Marylou and wants revenge! But while he is angry all the flowers around start to fade, as the Pretty Flower Contest just began...

24.SummaryEnglish: Sarah, who must handle a huge order for the bakery, decides to use the magic mirror to duplicate some cream puffs... But it's Dadaping who has been cloned!

25.SummaryEnglish: Nonoping, pursed by Romi, hits her with his magic and breaks her magic wand. She suddenly says "No!" to everything asked of her, and refuses to catch him...

26.SummaryEnglish: While Heartsping and Gogoping are having an argument, Luvping throws love arrows all over Harmony Village, very dangerous for the Teeniepings...

27.SummaryEnglish: As Romi just received a new magic power and dreams to finds Happying, Giggleping creates strange phenomenons in all the city. But this strange Teenieping isn't like any other.

28.SummaryEnglish: Coolping, who used to live in a very cold place, is furious when his home is moved and wants revenge! Romi tries to catch him, while Giggleping tries to steal Tiny Heart Wing...

29.SummaryEnglish: Artping creates some very stranges phenomenas in the Heartrose Bakery : disapearing pigs, flying fishes... Quickly, he allies with Giggleping

30.SummaryEnglish: During a sleepover, Romi discovers Maya's greatest dream. With the help of her superpowers, she is gonna realize it!

31.SummaryEnglish: In a picnic with Romi and the Royal Teeniepings, Gogoping is accused to have eaten all the blueberries. It's Mugeoping, who played a trick on him...

32.SummaryEnglish: While Romi, Maya and Marylou are tidying up the school library, Oppoping turns them over... It's gonna be difficult to live upside down!

33.SummaryEnglish: Trying to prevent Giggleping using to magic mirror to clone herself, Romi is cloned, and she has a lot of difficulties working with her clones...

34.SummaryEnglish: Zipping, the super-fast Teenieping, allies with Giggleping to defeat Romi. A race begins in all the bakery, but Romi can't catch him : he's too fast!

35.TitleEnglish: Do You Wanna Be A Baby?
35.SummaryEnglish: Lena, Cindy, and Hani are hanging in the garden. When she says she doesn't like babies, she is hit by Bebeping and becomes and a baby. This Teenieping hits everyone, including Romi!

36.SummaryEnglish: On a normal day, two aliens arrives at Harmony Village, and decides to conquer the city. But it won't be an easy task, as they aren't very lucky...

37.SummaryEnglish: Kojaping, who can make people fall asleep and see their dreams, use his powers against Romi, with the help of Giggleping. How will the Royal Teeniepings save her?

38.SummaryEnglish: Romi and Lena, who are arguing, are glued together by Stickping. It won't be easy for Romi to catch her, as she can't get away from Lena!

39.SummaryEnglish: Curieping, who can extend anything with his magnifying glass, creates a giant rabbit for Giggleping so they can have fun traveling and scaring all of Harmony Village!

40.SummaryEnglish: Romi is organizing a big festival with all the Teeniepings she has caught. Giggleping, watches everything, and would like to be part of it...

41.SummaryEnglish: In Harmony Village, Toyping transforms everything he finds into very little toys. Ian, Kyle, and Jun became dolls as Luca is organizing a wedding!

42.SummaryEnglish: Wannabeping meets Giggleping. She quickly allies with him and decides to trick Romi, pretending to be his father, but Romi notices that something is wrong...

43.SummaryEnglish: Flaping, the garden of Emotion Kingdom, is furious when he sees Lena tearing out a flower. To punish her, she transforms her and her friends into flowers!

44.SummaryEnglish: Princess Romi catches two very cute Teeniepings: Noraping and his little brother, Noriping. But as Noriping wants to play with his brother, Noraping tries to get rid of him...

45.SummaryEnglish: Romi, who is once again fighting Giggleping, recovers a piece that Giggleping dropped, which leads her to finally discover her true identity. She must fight her...

46.SummaryEnglish: Romi, who just recovered Happying, discovers a new Teenieping, Ahuuping, who makes people unlucky because she is sad. Romi will need Happying to convince her to stop!

47.SummaryEnglish: During the break, the Teeniepings meet Shushping, a very hard-working Teenieping! To capture him, Romi will have to be very quiet!

48.SummaryEnglish: On a very hot day, Romi decides to eat some ice cream with her friends. But she quickly faces Kkongkkongping, the brother of Coolping...

49.SummaryEnglish: Princess Romi can't capture Jjiritping. This Teenieping can throw electricity, control electric devices and even travel through electricity! The whole city feels very energic today!

50.SummaryEnglish: On the beach of Harmony Village is a strange guest: a giant whale who looks sick. The Royal Teeniepings, while exploring the whale, meets Holloping...

51.TitleEnglish: In The Name Of The Royalpings
51.SummaryEnglish: The first part of the battle against Egoping, who is invading the city with her giant flower. Princess Romi can't catch her, and a Teenieping decides to sacrifice to save her...

52.SummaryEnglish: The second part of the battle against Egoping. Romi finally catches her, but as she has caught all the Teenieping of the city, she has to return to the Emotion Kingdom.
